title: Clip # 1 - Jumanji Welcome to the Jungle - Hippo Scene

json.text: You guys this can't actually be happening. Maybe we are all in a coma.
-Together? We're all in a coma together?   -It's the only explanation! That old game machine must have electrocuted all of us and...
-You better get in there and save her!    -I'm not getting in there! You get in there!
I'm not going anywhere, I got a backpack on! You don't get in water with a backpack!
-That was so intense. I, like, can't even with this place.
-What just happen to you?   -I got eaten by a rhino, and then I fell, like, a thousand feet from the sky.
-Yeah that's what it looked like.   -That was a hippo.
They're omnivorous. They are fast as a horse over short distances, and they have the bite force of 8100 Newtons.
-How do I know this?   -You're an expert in zoology.
-What!?   -I'm still an old fat guy, right?   -I'm afraid so.
Wait, why is everybody okay with this?
Bethany get up, Bethany get up!
